  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The mission of the Utah Support Advocates for Recovery Awareness (USARA) is to connect and inspire communities to advocate for addiction recovery. We envision a Utah where recovery community and connection are recognized as the most valuable assets for people to recover from addiction. We provide non-clinical, peer-based recovery support services to individuals and families in Utah seeking recovery from substance use disorders.</narrative>
